-03T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"幫香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"2daad1058e5961b2becb12035e1fd0d076b79f51","tid":1535270,"uid":7043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"人地行路落黎係要耐小小"},{"pid":"b5305cc28137bee167652e7d19de6b3c75abe4d8","tid":1535270,"uid":305794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:53:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">知道大家都攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地唔可以放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想贏既就入黎睇一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535187/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535187/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"56773c60e33c6d306eeb91288547d1ad30afa4a1","tid":1535270,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"下年都未黎到喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc0aff0e1423b154a32454105b6abb4bbff9053","tid":1535270,"uid":128102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:54:32.000Z","msg":"我淨係想知 <br />\n點解要咁遠揾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2bc67eda11fe80b9a7646e47a3d76604ce2ef1","tid":1535270,"uid":50327,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:55:34.000Z","msg":"黎整切糕？"},{"pid":"81cc4290e5e7604f80e6193ddeca2590d80170ef","tid":1535270,"uid":280326,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"他們要奶粉？黃道益？定胃藥？"},{"pid":"66a5def936efb857e61a1e105d378188d94713de","tid":1535270,"uid":316370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"